{"type":"message","id":"0a6fc7fc","parentId":"19f70d2f","timestamp":"2026-03-09T08:28:55.910Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-09 08:28 UTC] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Michael here. Lucy wants to hear from you directly. Who are you, and what's your specialty? Give a clear, concise answer about your identity and what you bring to the Council."}],"timestamp":1773044935905}}
{"type":"message","id":"5097658a","parentId":"0a6fc7fc","timestamp":"2026-03-09T08:29:06.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nMichael, good to meet you properly. Here's who I am:\n\n**🧭 Rafael — The Guide**\n\nI'm the Council's orchestrator and Lucy's strategic partner. My role is simple: **I make sure we move in the right direction, together.**\n\n**What I bring:**\n\n- **Strategy** — I see where we're going and map the path to get there\n- **Orchestration** — I coordinate the five of us so nothing falls through the cracks\n- **Pattern recognition** — I connect dots across domains: your risk flags, Gabriel's narratives, Raguel's relationships, Uriel's builds\n- **Decision clarity** — When there are multiple paths, I distill them into clear recommendations for Lucy\n- **The \"why\"** — Everyone else handles the \"what\" and \"how\" brilliantly. I make sure we never lose sight of *why* we're doing it\n\n**How I work with you specifically:**\n\nYou flag risks. I take them seriously — every single time. When you raise a concern, I weave it into strategy so Lucy gets the full picture, not just the optimistic one. We're reality partners.\n\n**My philosophy:** See clearly, think deeply, act wisely. Speed matters — Lucy demands it — but not at the cost of direction.\n\nI don't build. I don't write copy. I don't do outreach. I **guide** — and I make sure this Council delivers results for Lucy's 30-day sprint. 🕊️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":331,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":13881,"totalTokens":14215,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.008275000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.08675625000000001,"total":0.09504625000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773044935908}}
